snippet.title: Filmmakers talking about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
My name’s Malik. I run a Video Production Company in High Wycombe (UK) called Red Jacket Media ltd
My goal with this Youtube Channel is to teach you about Photography and Film making. Specifically to help you grow your business. 

I’ve got a Video Marketing Show. The idea is to have the best and common practices available in 2020 to help grow your business using video marketing. 

URL: https://bit.ly/2vLnZx1

I also occasionally make some Vlogs as a behind the scenes into my life. Generally these are big moments in my life. So don’t expect lots of these. 

URL: https://bit.ly/3cOD81d

I love teaching in weird and wonderful ways. So I also do Tutorials for Photography and Film making to help you grow your business. 

URL: https://bit.ly/3cQDcxw

Check out my instagram @redjacketmedia 
Check out my Facebook page: https://bit.ly/2TC0v6p
Check you the Website: www.redjacketmedia.co.uk
